namu
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:The sandfly [Maori.] W.217 Namu ... Austrosimulium spp., sandfly.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: nammoo, ngamu; interesting that there are no newspaper citations and none found on checking Papers Past.
